    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Ego <persName key="#Count" ref="#people/4290">Rainulphus</persName> Dei
                        gratia <rs key="#Count">Comes</rs>, juro et promitto tibi Domino <persName
                            key="#Bishops" ref="#people/5007">Stationi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">Episcopo</rs>, quod usque ad Kal. 5. Octobr. primo
                        venturas assignabo tibi formam proprietatem tuae <rs key="#Mother_churches"
                            >Ecclesiae</rs>, et in possessionem ponam te, et eandem Ecclesiam de
                        toto <rs key="#Feudum">feudo</rs>, quod <persName key="#milesOf"><name
                                ref="Balcolinus">Balcolinus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#milesOf">miles</rs> tenuit de intus <placeName
                            key="#Cities #City_territory" ref="#places/3483"><geogName
                                ref="#estates/3060">Cajatiam</geogName></placeName>, et de foris
                        infra <rs key="#City_territory">finem</rs> ejusdem <rs key="#Cities"
                            >Civitatis</rs>, praeter <rs key="#Houses">domum</rs>, quae est infra
                            <rs key="#Fortifications">Castrum</rs> et praeter <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terram</rs>, quam <persName><name
                                ref="Amalgarius">Malcerius</name></persName> vendidit <persName
                            key="#childOf"><name ref="Rogerius f. Alardi">Rogerio</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filio</rs>
                        <persName><name ref="Alardus de Albiniano">Altardi de
                            Albiniano</name></persName>, et preter <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terram</rs>, de qua <persName><name ref="Garialdus"
                            >Giraldus</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Gismundus"
                                >Gismundus</name></persName> singularem calumniam moverunt, quae est
                        in loco <placeName ref="#places/5122">Carpanito</placeName>. Si nos enim
                        praejudicium providerimus sine fraude, quam tibi promittamus, et post
                        assignationem, et donationem . . . . . . et idem Cajaccianae Ecclesiae
                        fecero de eodem feudo, et non ero in facto, concilio, seu consensu, quod tu,
                        vel tui successores in toto, vel in parte perdatis, sed adjuvabo eandem
                        Ecclesiam, et te, tuosque successores, illud tenere, defendere, contra omnes
                        homines, qui in toto, vel in parte auferant, vel auferri consentiant, neque
                        faciam. Haec omnia observabo sine fraude, et malo ingenio. Et sic Dominus me
                        adjuvet, et haec sancta quatuor Evangelia Domini. Hoc actum est coram Domino
                            <persName key="#Witness #Princeps" ref="#people/3042">Roberto</persName>
                        <placeName ref="#places/173">Capuano</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">Principe</rs>, et Dom. <persName key="#Witness #Bishops"
                            ref="#people/5008">Henrico</persName>
                        <placeName ref="#places/728">Agathe</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">Episcopo</rs>, <persName key="#Witness #Deacons #Abbots"
                            ref="#people/5009">Joanne</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">Abbate</rs>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">Diacono</rs> ejus, <persName key="#Witness #Advocatus"
                            ref="#people/5010">Riccardo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Advocatus">Advocato</rs>, <persName key="#Witness #milesOf"><name
                                ref="Zoffus Curolus">Zoffo Curolo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#milesOf">milite</rs>, <persName key="#Witness #Judge"
                            ref="#people/3037">Filippo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">Judice</rs> Capuano, et <persName key="#Witness #Judge"
                            ref="#people/5011">Ursone</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">Judice</rs> Agathae, et <rs key="#Priests">Presbytero</rs>
                        <persName key="#Witness #Chaplain #Priests" ref="#people/5012"
                            >Hisembrando</persName> praefati Principis <rs key="#Chaplain"
                            >Capellano</rs>, <persName key="#Witness #Priests" ref="#people/5013"
                            >Petro</persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">Presbytero</rs> Cajaccianae Ecclesiae, et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Deacons" ref="#people/5014">Guglielmo</persName> ejusdem
                        Ecclesiae <rs key="#Deacons">Diacono</rs>. </ab>
